# Changing game settings (Suhail)

## Actor (Player)

The player playing the game

## Pre-conditions

Have the settings window open and display all options.

## Main Flow

1) Player chooses the setting that they wish to change. I.e sound, brightness, etc.
2) A slider appears that the player can adjust accordingly
3) The player clicks on the button to save settings.

## Alternate Flow

1) The player does not save the changes to their settings.
2) The settings are reverted to their default state.

## Postconditions

The player has successfully changed the settings of the game to their liking.
